roles_path=./roles
ansible-galaxy install ROLENAME
ansible-galaxy install -r requirements.txt
to create role directory sructure use - ansible-galaxy role init <role name>

how to debug a playbook -
 
command to install yamllint - pip3 install yamllimt
command to checck the syntax of yaml - yamllint <filename>
command to check if playbook is fine - ansible-playbook playbook.yml --syntax-check
command to install ansible-lint - pip3 install ansible-lint
command to know how to write best playbook - ansible-lint playbook.yml
